data.text: @healthgovau 'Booster' was dropped last year - we were all told we needed a third dose. No wonder the optional 'Booster' take up is slow if you're still using that language in some places. Shouldn't your graphics/messaging match the language from your CMO and the WHO? Three doses needed.

@healthgovau How many dead within minutes or days after experiment injected? How many suffering life long injuries after experiment injection? How many children have you killed with these experiments which you where told where NOT safe for children? How many unborn have your murdered?

@healthgovau How many deaths after vax, men, women and children? How many injured for life after vax, men, women and children? Why are these experiments which have clearly failed still being enforced?
